                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="content-section">
                        <h2>Why Choose our IGCSE/IB Online Platform?</h2>
                        <div class="programs-table">
                            <table>
                                <thead>
                                    <tr>
                                        <th>Features</th>
                                        <th>Why Choose Manya Education Platform?</th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>Expert Tutors</td>
                                        <td>The team consists of highly qualified as well as experienced specialists in IGCSE/IB subjects as well as curriculum. They bring a strong understanding for both international exam format as well as educational standards.</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>Personalized Learning</td>
                                        <td>The lessons are tailored to meet individual students' needs, which ensures customized learning plan, which targets areas of improvement as well as enhances our strengths.</td>
