                                        <td>Proven methods to ace both internal tests and their final exams, with strong focus on results-driven preparation and guaranteed grade improvement.</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>Interactive Online Tools</td>
                                        <td>Interactive tools which include whiteboards, video lessons, quizzes and study resources, students engage more deeply with the content as well as enjoy a more interactive as well as dynamic learning experience.</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>Comprehensive Resource Hub</td>
                                        <td>Manya provides extensive learning materials which includes previous year papers and practice tests which are designed to align with the IGCSE/IB syllabus, which helps in rigorous preparation.</td>
