                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="content-section">
                        <h2>Flexible Tutoring Packages for IGCSE/IB Success</h2>
                        <div class="programs-table">
                            <table>
                                <thead>
                                    <tr>
                                        <th>Focused Grade Improvement Tutoring</th>
                                        <th>Regular Tuition</th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>Our personalized tutoring sessions are to target particular weaknesses, helping students improve their grades effectively and quickly. This is possible with tailored learning plans with focused academic growth.</td>
                                        <td>Stay on track with regular and ongoing tutoring for building a strong foundation and for ensuring academic progress. With flexible sessions to provide continuous support for coursework, homework and exam preparation</td>
                                    </tr>
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="content-section">
                        <h2>Get an A/A+ Guaranteed</h2>
                        <div class="benefits-grid">
                            <div class="benefit-item">
                                <h3>Concept Clarity</h3>
                                <ol>
                                    <li>Deep Understanding of Key concepts: Students to gain thorough understanding of fundamental concepts for each subject and clear any doubts and build strong academic foundation.</li>
                                    <li>Step-by-Step Approach: Tutors break down the complex topics into manageable and smaller steps, which helps students to grasp difficult concepts easily.</li>
                                    <li>Interactive Learning: With engaging explanations, visual aids as well as real-world applications, learning is made more accessible and clarity of concepts is prioritized.</li>
                                </ol>
                            </div>
                            <div class="benefit-item">
                                <h3>Inclusive Teaching & Learning</h3>
                                <ol>
                                    <li>Tailored Learning Experience: Whether visual learner, auditory learner, or prefer hands-on activities, tutors adapt their teaching skills to suit individual style.</li>
                                    <li>Support for Diverse Needs: Inclusive teaching methods which cater to students with varied learning needs, ensuring everyone succeeds equally.</li>
                                    <li>Building Confidence: Our supportive tutors create a safe and inclusive learning environment where students can ask questions, participate and grow academically!</li>
                                </ol>
                            </div>
                            <div class="benefit-item">
                                <h3>Exam Style Practice</h3>
                                <ol>
                                    <li>Realistic Exam Simulations: We offer regular exam-style practice questions, mock tests and previous papers for ensuring students are familiar with exam format and question types.</li>
                                    <li>Time Management Skills: Practice under timed conditions for enhancement of speed and accuracy, to be prepared for exam day stress.</li>
                                    <li>Targeted Focus on Weak Areas: Detailed analysis of mock exam results, identification of areas where students need to improve and focus practice on those weak spots.</li>
                                </ol>
                            </div>
                            <div class="benefit-item">
                                <h3>Feedback & Support</h3>
                                <ol>
                                    <li>Regular Progress Assessments: Our tutors provide regular assessments as well as progress reports, and give students and parents detailed insights into areas of improvement.</li>
                                    <li>Constructive Feedback: We offer specific, actionable feedback after each session as well as mock tests.</li>
                                    <li>Ongoing Support for Improvement: Regular check-ins and adjustments to learning plan, which ensures the students stay on track and work towards progress.</li>
                                </ol>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                 <!-- Right Content - Form -->
                 <div class="content-right">
                    <form class="enquiry-form" id="enquiryForm" action="/submit-igcse-ib-tutoring"  method="POST">
                        <h3>Planning to study abroad?</h3>
                        <p>Get free 1-on-1 counselling with our experts</p>
            
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <input type="text" id="firstName" name="firstName" required>
                            <label for="firstName">First Name</label>
                        </div>
            
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <input type="text" id="lastName" name="lastName" required>
                            <label for="lastName">Last Name</label>
                        </div>
            
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
                            <label for="email">Email</label>
                        </div>
            
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <input type="tel" id="mobile" name="mobile" pattern="[0-9]{10}" required>
                            <label for="mobile">Mobile No. (10 digits)</label>
                        </div>
            
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <select id="program" name="program" required>
                                <option value="">Select Program</option>
                                <option value="GMAT">GMAT</option>
                                <option value="GRE">GRE</option>
                                <option value="IELTS">IELTS</option>
                            </select>
                            <label for="program">Select Program</label>
                        </div>
            
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <select id="mode" name="mode" required>
                                <option value="">Select Mode</option>
                                <option value="Classroom">Classroom Coaching</option>
                                <option value="Online">Online Coaching</option>
                            </select>
                            <label for="mode">Select Mode</label>
                        </div>
            
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <select id="city" name="city" required>
                                <option value="">Select City</option>
                                <option value="Noida">Noida</option>
                                <option value="Delhi">Delhi</option>
                                <option value="Gurgaon">Gurgaon</option>
                            </select>
                            <label for="city">Select City</label>
                        </div>
            
                        <div class="checkbox-group">
                            <input type="checkbox" id="authorize" name="authorize" required>
                            <label for="authorize">I authorize Manya - The Princeton Review to contact me even if my number is registered with DND to assist with my enquiry and get regular updates through SMS/Whatsapp.</label>
                        </div>

                        <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Submit</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <%- include('partials/Footer') %>
    </div>

